Q28. Initialize one String type of array and print the elements using for each loop.

Answer :- 

import java.util.*;

class Q28
{
	public static void main(String args[])
	{
		String arr[] = {"Red","Blue","Green"};
		
		for(String a : arr)
		{
			System.out.println(a);
		}
	}
}

